reviewText: Move on. This is not an instructional video.

I'm planning a sexual massage for my girlfriend, I bought The joy of erotic massage , the art of sensual massage and this DVDs, journey into sensual massage.. The first  2 were great and gave me everything I was looking for. This was a waste of time and money.. No instruction, just a video of a poorly given short massage , ugh.. Feel ripped off, threw in garbage

So I got this for my boyfriend and I because I feel like he sucks at giving massages and he says the same about me lol.. Anyway When I watched the dvd there were some good techniques, but I wish that there would have been more educational, I felt like it was a lot of acting in the dvd and was waiting for them to start going at it lol ... Not bad but not 100% awesome! I received this product at a discounted price for my honest review.

hoping for more of an educational dvd on massage. for aromatherapy or certain areas. was a little risque for my task in educational material. it taught some things but was interesting to say the least.

This PleasurePosition Journey into Sensual Massage by Kymberly Jane came packaged appropriately with a secure cover and the DVD worked properly.  I have to say I was thinking this DVD was going to be more of an instructional type of learning how to do sensual massages to one another.  Instead I felt it to be a more of soft sexual introduction with the opposite sex.  It was disappointing to me but perhaps it would be different from another person's point of view.  I did receive this at a discount for my unbiased review.  This is my opinion of this product.
Not worth the money. I'm self tought on giving massages and these techniques were far from pleasurable. Great DVD on applying oil..
